name: Not Happy Wheels
description:
TAB TO PAUSE

This game was made for the Brackeys Game Jam 2022.1, based on the theme "It is not real".

My interpretation of this theme was to make a knock off version of an existing game. Welcome to Not Happy Wheels! a game that may seem to be Happy Wheels, but I can assure you it is not real.

Controls are the same as the original but you can also view them in the character select menu.

I made most of this game solo but my friend, Reispfannenfresser, helped out by creating a couple of levels. Huge thanks to him.

if you play this Not Happy Wheels 5 game more than five times, you will be more and more involved, why the game is so addictive we will not discuss.
